description: Lists detectors (the instances of a detector model).

parameters.name: detectorModelName
parameters.description: The name of the detector model whose detectors (instances) are listed.

nested_items.name: detectorSummaries
nested_items.description: A list of summary information about the detectors (instances).

nested_items.name: detectorModelName
nested_items.description: The name of the detector model that created this detector (instance).

nested_items.name: keyValue
nested_items.description: The value of the key (identifying the device or system) that caused the creation of this detector (instance).

nested_items.name: detectorModelVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the detector model that created this detector (instance).

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the detector (instance) was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The time the detector (instance) was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token that you can use to return the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.
